# 5. Policy Stress Test — Realistic Exploitation Scenario

## Purpose
Validate executive governance resilience under real-world exploitation.

## Focus
- Governance quality  
- Assumption validity  
- Decision traceability  
- Evidence readiness  

Legal hold is automatic upon activation.

